Deploy hyper personalized AI agents that answer, sell, and support across phone, WhatsApp, and web. Purpose built to reduce support load, increase revenue, and deliver 24/7 engagement at enterprise scale.
Ulai is a full-stack platform to build and deploy intelligent voice and text agents with real-time control, analytics, and enterprise-grade performance.
Create intelligent voice agents that hold natural conversations, automate support and sales, and never miss a call.
Deploy chat agents with rich functionality and deep interface control—seamless to build, effortless to manage.
Build, deploy, and manage lifelike AI agents—powered by advanced voice infrastructure and developer-ready flexibility.
Low latency architecture ensures voice and text responses feel instant and natural just like human conversations.
Your agents listen like pros pausing when interrupted, resuming when needed, and never talking over users.
Connect globally with support for 30+ languages and dialects, optimized for both voice and text across channels.
Choose from thousands of lifelike voice models or integrate your own TTS engine to deliver hyper-personalized audio.
Sync agents directly with documentation or help centers for always updated responses.
Understand user intent, personalize replies with historical context, and adapt the journey as the interaction unfolds.
Choose from thousands of realistic voices, or bring your own TTS provider.
Personalize interactions using customer history and intent prediction.
From WhatsApp to Web Chat to voice calls Ulai ensures consistent conversations across every touchpoint.
Trigger workflows, automate tasks, and execute backend logic—all from within the chat or call on any channel.
Stay enterprise ready with complete interaction logs, audit trails, and built-in compliance features.
Deploy a single AI agent that handles calls and live chat together—no extra setup, just extra power.
Deliver human like, two way conversations across WhatsApp, webchat, and more. Personalized, contextual, and always on without the need for manual workflows.
Design, deploy, and monitor intelligent voice and text agents , all without writing a single line of code.
Ulai empowers businesses to deploy intelligent AI agents with the speed, flexibility, and resilience required for mission critical operations.
Always-on availability with fault-tolerant architecture for peak loads.
Deliver human-like interactions with voice and text agents powered by Ulai’s proprietary ASR, STT/TTS stack, and memory-enabled LLMs—trained for empathy and accuracy.
Encrypted, GDPR-ready, and audit-trail backed for safe, compliant conversations.
Adapts to healthcare, D2C, BFSI, travel, and more—no extra setup needed.
Ulai scales effortlessly for real-time interactions from hundreds to millions with zero performance drop.
One platform. Multiple channels. Ulai offers unified customer journeys across WhatsApp, Web, Instagram, FB Messenger, and Voice—maintaining consistency and context.
Trigger backend actions, run custom functions, or pull real-time data mid-conversation. Ulai’s low code interface allows non developers to orchestrate business logic easily.
Integrate with CRMs, helpdesks, commerce engines, or internal APIs—Ulai connects natively with tools like Shopify, Freshdesk, Zoho, and more.
Remembers context across tools and sessions for seamless conversations.
Enhance agent productivity and deliver seamless 24/7 customer support through intelligent automation.
Discover how our voice AI platform empowers you to build, test, deploy, and monitor intelligent voice agents with ease and precision.
Utilize the voice AI API and our intuitive agent builder to create custom voice AI agents effortlessly.
Perform comprehensive agent testing with built-in test LLM features to ensure seamless handling of edge cases.
Easily deploy your agents to phone calls, web calls, SMS, and more.
Track success rates, latency, and user sentiment through the call history dashboard. Quickly identify failed calls.
Build Enterprise-grade Agents at Scale
Startups Get Started Free
Explore how AI agents work, how Ulai integrates with your business, and how our AI call platform meets your needs.
Build smarter conversations. Deploy AI voice and chat agents that understand, respond, and deliver—instantly.

Ulai is a full stack agentic AI platform that helps businesses deploy intelligent voice and text agents for sales, support, and engagement. Built for scale, speed, and flexibility. Ulai powers real-time conversations across phone, chat, and messaging channels.
Email: hello@ulai.in
